Christopher Rosser, ónyé a maara nke ọma site na aha egwu ya bụ Quay Global, bụ ónyé na-emepụta ihe ndekọ America
A maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya na onye na-eti egwu Lil Baby
Enwere ike ịmata ọrụ ya site na mkpado mmepụta "Cook that shit up, Quay!".
Rosser malitere imepụta egwu mgbè ọ dị afọ itoolu
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Columbia.
Rosser mere aha màkà onwé ya site n'ịmepụta egwu "My Dawg" nke Lil Baby, nke e depụtara na Billboard Hot 100 ma RIAA kwadoro Platinum

Mgbe "My Dawg" hụrụ ihe ịga nke ọma, N'Quay bịanyere aka na ụlọ ọrụ ndekọ nke Atlanta Quality Control Music n'ọnwa Ọktoba 2017. Egwú ndị ọzọ a ma ama nke Lil Baby mepụtara bụ "Life Goes On", "Pure Cocaine", na "Woah", nke niile gosipụtara na Hot 100, nke ikpeazụ nké ruru n'ọkwa 15.
